name: CFComparisonResult
desc: Constants returned by comparison functions, indicating whether a value is equal to, less than, or greater than another value.

items.name: case compareLessThan
items.desc: Returned by a comparison function if the first value is less than the second value.

items.name: case compareEqualTo
items.desc: Returned by a comparison function if the first value is equal to the second value.

items.name: case compareGreaterThan
items.desc: Returned by a comparison function if the first value is greater than the second value.
